Title: Fast Travel Teleporter (Free)
Description: Adds the Glyphic Relocator, a useful little gadget that lets you fast travel to over 100 spots in the game. This version has all destinations unlocked.
Author: Gibdos

Items.Name: Glyphic Relocator
Items.Description: Warps party to your choice of 123 destinations.

Data.Message: Look what I found inbetween some old books.
It can be good to have a map on hand while exploring.
But if you don't have one, don't worry! Sometimes the best adventures are had while exploring blind.
And any area you see in a region while you don't have a map will be filled in automatically later when you do get the map.
Now where did I put that...
Choose a page! (Based on Map Name, not Home Point)
